videos.description: UConn passes the ball around the 3-point line, which leads to Dorka Juhasz getting to the bucket for a reverse layup.

videos.description: Paige Bueckers helps keep UConn up in the first half as she drops 12 points in the second quarter.

videos.description: Paige Bueckers scores 34 points on 15-of-19 shooting in UConn's 95-80 win over Arkansas.
